		<div>Another option would be to adjust the item so it no longer trivializes the game so bad. Instead of leaving the item unchanged or removing it completely they could have just as easily put the same restriction on, say a mana robe, that compares to say, a mod rod. You are still allowed to use it but now a mana stone or mana robe can only be clicked once ever 2 min or so. It reduces the overpowering aspect without reducing it's usefullness to absolute 0.<br />
